  "description": "<p><strong>来自黑莓CEO<span id=\"intelliTxt\"> Thorsten Heins确认的消息，公司的7英寸平板产品PlayBook将不会升级到BlackBerry 10系统，原因是这款平板在运行BB10时体验不佳，不能令人满意，因此干脆取消掉。</span></strong><span id=\"intelliTxt\">这一决定会让许多PlayBook用户失望，而下一代产品的推出也还遥遥无期。黑莓官方也没有透露是否会提供新的功能增加和升级，但修补工作应该会持续。最近一个季度，黑莓PlayBook平板电脑售出了10万台，而智能手机卖出680万台，只是后者的零头。<br /></span></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ded37f4/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242823.htm&amp;t=%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93PlayBook%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0BB10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242823.htm&amp;t=%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93PlayBook%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0BB10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242823.htm&amp;t=%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93PlayBook%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0BB10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242823.htm&amp;t=%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93PlayBook%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0BB10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242823.htm&amp;t=%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93PlayBook%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%